12#ifndef MODULES_RTP_RTCP_SOURCE_RTCP_PACKET_BYE_H_
13#define MODULES_RTP_RTCP_SOURCE_RTCP_PACKET_BYE_H_
14
15#include <string>
16#include <vector>
17
18#include "modules/rtp_rtcp/source/rtcp_packet.h"
19
20namespace webrtc {
21namespace rtcp {
22class CommonHeader;
23
24class Bye : public RtcpPacket {
25 public:
26 static constexpr uint8_t kPacketType = 203;
27
28 Bye();
29 ~Bye() override;
30
31 // Parse assumes header is already parsed and validated.
32 bool Parse(const CommonHeader& packet);
33
34 bool SetCsrcs(std::vector<uint32_t> csrcs);
35 void SetReason(std::string reason);
36
37 const std::vector<uint32_t>& csrcs() const { return csrcs_; }
38 const std::string& reason() const { return reason_; }
39
40 size_t BlockLength() const override;
41
42 bool Create(uint8_t* packet,
43 size_t* index,
44 size_t max_length,
45 PacketReadyCallback callback) const override;
46
47 private:
48 static const int kMaxNumberOfCsrcs = 0x1f - 1; // First item is sender SSRC.
49
50 std::vector<uint32_t> csrcs_;
51 std::string reason_;
52};
53
54} // namespace rtcp
55} // namespace webrtc
56#endif // MODULES_RTP_RTCP_SOURCE_RTCP_PACKET_BYE_H_
